{"id":694477,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abel_Ferrara","text":"e=\"preserve\">Abel Ferrara (born July 19, 1951) is an American movie maker. In his movies there is provocative and controversial content. His best known movies are \"Ms. 45\" (1981), \"Cat Chaser\" (1989), \"King of New York\" (1990), \"Dangerous Game\" and \"The Funeral\" (1996).\nFerrara later directed the movie \"'R Xmas\" (2001). He directed the movie \"Mary\" in 2005. That was about religion and Jesus Christ.\nFerrara was born in The Bronx, New York City.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"United_States","surface_form":"American","offset":53},{"uri":"Movie","surface_form":"movie","offset":62},{"uri":"Controversy","surface_form":"controversial","offset":114},{"uri":"Ms._45","surface_form":"Ms. 45","offset":164},{"uri":"Cat_Chaser","surface_form":"Cat Chaser","offset":181},{"uri":"King_of_New_York","surface_form":"King of New York","offset":202},{"uri":"Dangerous_Game_(movie)","surface_form":"Dangerous Game","offset":229},{"uri":"The_Funeral_(movie)","surface_form":"The Funeral","offset":250},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"directed","offset":285},{"uri":"%27R_Xmas","surface_form":"'R Xmas","offset":305},{"uri":"Mary_(2005_movie)","surface_form":"Mary","offset":345},{"uri":"Religion","surface_form":"religion","offset":375},{"uri":"Jesus","surface_form":"Jesus Christ","offset":388},{"uri":"The_Bronx","surface_form":"The Bronx","offset":422},{"uri":"New_York_City","surface_form":"New York City","offset":433}]}